---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Temecula Wine Country">
  <Navbar />

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-6xl font-serif tracking-tight mb-8">About Temecula Wine Country</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none text-lg">
      <p>Temecula Valley is one of Southern California’s premier wine destinations, home to over 40 wineries nestled in the rolling hills of Riverside County.</p>
      
      <p>With its unique microclimate and diverse soil types, the region produces an impressive range of wines — from elegant Chardonnays and bold Cabernet Sauvignons to crisp sparkling wines and Rhône-style blends.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mt-12 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>This directory exists to help visitors discover the best wineries in Temecula Valley, whether you're planning your first visit or looking for new favorites.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mt-12 mb-4">Visit Responsibly</h2>
      <p>Always designate a driver or use rideshare services. Many wineries offer non-alcoholic options and beautiful grounds perfect for picnics and events.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
